x ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"fcdb\">Table of Contents</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"d586\"><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#9492\" rel=\"noopener\">Project Introduction</a><br/><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#5a51\" rel=\"noopener\">Data Collection<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#612c\" rel=\"noopener\">Web Scraping Headlines<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#3937\" rel=\"noopener\">Sentiment Analysis<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#5c55\" rel=\"noopener\">Compound Sentiment Score<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#989f\" rel=\"noopener\">Data Aggregation<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#0a20\" rel=\"noopener\">Key Findings from the Analyses<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#5a9c\" rel=\"noopener\">Compound Sentiment Trend Over Time<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#f01a\" rel=\"noopener\">Sentiment on Holidays<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#d1be\" rel=\"noopener\">Average Sentiment by Weekday<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#da15\" rel=\"noopener\">Interpretation of Findings<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#9f9c\" rel=\"noopener\">Conclusion<br/></a><a class=\"ah mq\" data-discover=\"true\" href=\"/@kmaurinjones/365-days-of-new-headlines-a-longitudinal-analysis-driven-by-data-science-b39c9ac9d8e5#23b7\" rel=\"noopener\">Final Thoughts</a></p><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"9492\">Project Introduction</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"5a61\">In today\u2019s digital age, we\u2019re inundated with news from countless sources, making it challenging to grasp the overall emotional tone of the media we consume. Over the past year, I ran a project called <strong class=\"mt gr\">DailyNewsDriftCanada</strong>, aimed at analyzing and visualizing the sentiment of news headlines from major Canadian media outlets. By monitoring these sentiments over time, the project sought to provide insights into the evolving media landscape, helping readers understand how news sentiment fluctuates across different sources and periods. In this article, I\u2019ll get into the conceptual aspects of the pipeline behind the project, detailing how data was collected, processed, and analyzed to reveal sentiment trends in Canadian news headlines. I\u2019ll also present key findings from the analyses conducted during the project\u2019s duration.</p><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"5a51\">Data Collection</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"7a9b\">The foundation of DailyNewsDriftCanada lies in collecting news headlines from various Canadian media outlets, specifically <strong class=\"mt gr\">CBC News</strong>, <strong class=\"mt gr\">CTV News</strong>, and <strong class=\"mt gr\">Global News</strong>. To gather this data, web scraping techniques were employed to automatically extract the latest headlines from the websites of these news organizations.</p><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"612c\">Web Scraping Headlines</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"cb63\">Web scraping involves programmatically accessing web pages and extracting specific information \u2014 in this case, news headlines and their corresponding URLs. By scheduling these scraping scripts to run daily, the project consistently collected fresh data over the course of a year. Key considerations in this stage included:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"3f11\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Handling Different Website Structures</strong>: Each news website has a unique HTML structure, so custom scraping functions were implemented for each source to accurately extract headlines and URLs.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"d827\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Error Handling</strong>: The scraping functions included error handling mechanisms to ensure the program continued running smoothly even if one of the websites was temporarily inaccessible or changed its layout.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"5e96\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Data Storage</strong>: The collected data was stored in CSV files, organized by date, making it easy to manage and process later.</li></ul><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"3937\">Sentiment Analysis</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"d29d\">Once the headlines were collected, the next step was to determine their emotional tone using sentiment analysis.</p><h3 class=\"pe nu gq bg nv pf pg ph nz pi pj pk od nc pl pm pn ng po pp pq nk pr ps pt pu bl\" id=\"c5f1\">Understanding Sentiment Valence</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"7a1b\">Sentiment valence is a numerical scale ranging from <strong class=\"mt gr\">-1 to 1</strong> that quantifies the emotional tone of a text:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"e33e\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">-1</strong>: Represents extreme negativity.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"9e1b\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">0</strong>: Indicates neutrality.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"9043\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">1</strong>: Represents extreme positivity. Values closer to -1 or 1 signify stronger negative or positive sentiments, respectively, while values near 0 suggest a neutral tone.</li></ul><h3 class=\"pe nu gq bg nv pf pg ph nz pi pj pk od nc pl pm pn ng po pp pq nk pr ps pt pu bl\" id=\"9584\">Sentiment Analysis Model</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"384e\">The project utilized a <a class=\"ah mq\" href=\"https://huggingface.co/cardiffnlp/twitter-roberta-base-sentiment-latest\" rel=\"noopener ugc nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">pre-trained sentiment analysis model</a> from HuggingFace based on the <strong class=\"mt gr\">RoBERTa</strong> architecture, fine-tuned for sentiment classification tasks. This model is capable of assigning sentiment scores to text inputs, providing probabilities for categories like positive, negative, and neutral.</p><h3 class=\"pe nu gq bg nv pf pg ph nz pi pj pk od nc pl pm pn ng po pp pq nk pr ps pt pu bl\" id=\"eb1f\">Processing Headlines</h3><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"24bf\">For each headline:</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"2610\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Tokenization</strong>: The headline text was tokenized, converting it into a format suitable for the model.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"cf70\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Model Prediction</strong>: The model predicted the sentiment scores for the headline, providing probabilities for each sentiment category.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"a6b4\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Score Interpretation</strong>: The probabilities were converted into sentiment scores, and the most probable sentiment label was assigned to the headline.</li></ul><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"5c55\">Compound Sentiment Score</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"b612\">To obtain a single numerical value representing the sentiment of each headline, a compound score was calculated using the positive, negative, and neutral scores provided by the model. The formula is:</p><figure class=\"pw px py pz qa mf lx ly paragraph-image\"><div class=\"mg mh eo mi bi mj\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"lx ly pv\"><picture><source sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 1400w\" type=\"image/webp\"/><source data-testid=\"og\" sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/0*zsVav-x5RBQX2y4F.png 1400w\"/><img alt=\"\" class=\"bi lh mk c\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\" role=\"presentation\" width=\"700\"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class=\"ml mm mn lx ly mo mp bg b bh ab ee\">Sentiment Compound Score Equation</figcaption></figure><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"7705\">This compound score reflects the overall sentiment valence of the headline on the <strong class=\"mt gr\">-1 to 1</strong> scale.</p><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"989f\">Data Aggregation</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"72e0\">After calculating sentiment scores for individual headlines, the data was aggregated to analyze trends over time and across different news sources.</p><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu mv mw mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ng nh ni nj nk nl nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"3956\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Daily Aggregation</strong>: Headlines were grouped by date and source to compute average sentiment scores for each news outlet on a daily basis.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"7068\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Weekday Aggregation</strong>: Data was also aggregated based on the day of the week to understand patterns in sentiment across different weekdays.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"0538\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Holiday Analysis</strong>: Sentiment scores on Canadian holidays were examined to see if there were notable differences in news sentiment during these periods.</li></ul><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"0a20\">Key Findings from the Analyses</h2><p class=\"pw-post-body-paragraph mr ms gq mt b mu or mw mx my os na nb nc ot ne nf ng ou ni nj nk ov nm nn no gj bl\" id=\"9545\">Over the course of the project, several analyses were conducted to uncover patterns and trends in news sentiment. Here are some of the key findings:</p><h2 class=\"nt nu gq bg nv nw nx ny nz oa ob oc od oe of og oh oi oj ok ol om on oo op oq bl\" id=\"5a9c\">Compound Sentiment Trend Over Time</h2><figure class=\"pw px py pz qa mf lx ly paragraph-image\"><div class=\"mg mh eo mi bi mj\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"lx ly qb\"><picture><source sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*2wZJ3t_Eu47kmcQrjUnAew.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*2wZJ3t_Eu47kmcQrjUnAew.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*2wZJ3t_Eu47kmcQrjUnAew.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/1*2wZJ3t_Eu47kmcQrjUnAew.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/1*2wZJ3t_Eu47kmcQrjUnAew.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/f