strong class=\"mt gr\">Y-Axis</strong>: Compound sentiment scores between <strong class=\"mt gr\">-0.30</strong> and <strong class=\"mt gr\">0.05</strong>.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"0ee8\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Observations</strong>: \u2014 <strong class=\"mt gr\">Mean Sentiment</strong>: Approximately <strong class=\"mt gr\">-0.13</strong>. \u2014 <strong class=\"mt gr\">Median Sentiment</strong>: Close to <strong class=\"mt gr\">-0.14</strong>, indicating a consistent distribution. \u2014 <strong class=\"mt gr\">Trend Line</strong>: A slight positive trend over the year, suggesting a gradual reduction in negativity.</li><li class=\"mr ms gq mt b mu oz mw mx my pa na nb nc pb ne nf ng pc ni nj nk pd nm nn no ow ox oy bl\" id=\"7a96\"><strong class=\"mt gr\">Insight</strong>: CBC\u2019s headline sentiment starts around <strong class=\"mt gr\">-0.15</strong> and gradually trends upward, indicating a slight shift toward neutrality over the analyzed period.</li></ul><figure class=\"pw px py pz qa mf lx ly paragraph-image\"><div class=\"mg mh eo mi bi mj\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><div class=\"lx ly qb\"><picture><source sizes=\"(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/1*kP0Okd5Lru9SZJhVJ4eKmw.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*kP0Okd5Lru9SZJhVJ4eKmw.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/1*kP0Okd5Lru9SZJhVJ4eKmw.png 750w, h